OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778367993
OL,3,CTwo charged after man dies and dog
OL,4,Cstabbed in Burntwood
OL,6,FTwo people have been charged after the
OL,7,Fdeath of a man in Burntwood,
OL,8,FStaffordshire.
OL,10,FCorey Magnus, 27, from Burntwood, also
OL,11,Fknown as John Solomon, has been
OL,12,Fcharged with the murder of 32-year-old
OL,13,FSashon Richards-Brown.
OL,15,FDanielle Simpson, 33, also from
OL,16,FBurntwood has been charged with
OL,17,Fassisting an offender.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
