OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778367993
OL,3,CTwo charged after man dies and dog
OL,4,Cstabbed in Burntwood
OL,6,FStaffordshire police were called to
OL,7,FHazel Grove just before 9am on
OL,8,FThursday 5th May following reports of
OL,9,Fpeople fighting.
OL,11,FSashon Richards-Brown, of no fixed
OL,12,Faddress, was found with significant
OL,13,Finjuries at the scene. Nothing could
OL,14,Fbe done to save him and he was
OL,15,Fpronounced dead shortly after 10am.
OL,17,FA dog was taken to an emergency vet
OL,18,Ffor treatment following the incident
OL,19,Fand remains in a serious condition.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
